[31m-# Source[m
[31m-[m
[31m-This "Source" folder is where all of your files associated with this site will go[m
[31m-and is considered the root ('/') of your site.[m
[31m-This is also where all of your pages will be generated when using the [page subgenerator](#Subgenerator).[m
[31m-[m
[31m-## Pages[m
[31m-[m
[31m-Pages are the main driver for static sites and also determine your site's routes.[m
[31m-All page templates (except index.{jade,nunjucks}) should be placed in a folder named by your desired route.[m
[31m-For example, a contact page would most likely be loaded at the `/contact` route.[m
[31m-You would acheive this by creating the following structure:[m
[31m-[m
[31m-```[m
[31m-└── src[m
[31m-    └── contact[m
[31m-        └── index.{jade,nunjucks}[m
[31m-```[m
[31m-[m
