[31m-```[m
[31m-[m
[31m-This will create the structure you saw above:[m
[31m-[m
[31m-```[m
[31m-└── src[m
[31m-    └── about[m
[31m-        └── index.{jade,nunjucks}[m
[31m-```[m
[31m-[m
[31m-So when you boot up your site and go to `/about` you will see your new page.[m
